This is a kitbash 3d made using the wonderful works from
DangItBlobby, KillMeForPrizes, TheZomby,Moonjam and Jimmyzimms.
In this Remix you will find MKVII armored troops mounted on bikes for the 40K universe in 6-8mm scale.

The archive contains:
2 biker variants
2 sergeant variants
chaplain
librarian
captain
standard bearer
assault bike

If you found it useful for your army and would like to buy me a beer I will appreciate it.

Print ready for resin printers. Just import, make sure the base is on the print bed, slice then print. 2xAA and 0.02mm layer height reccommended.
These files are not intended for FDM slicers or printers.

Please bear in mind that these miniatures have extremely fragile parts despite my best efforts to make everything as solid as possible. Handle with care.

added unsupported files, all meshes were originally designed to be rotated 25 degrees backwards
